import { Input ,Form,FormGroup,Label,Button,FormText, Card } from "reactstrap";
import './FormComponent.css';

export function FormComponent2(params) {

    return(
        
      <Form inline>
      <FormGroup floating>
        <Input
          id="exampleEmail"
          name="email"
          placeholder="Email"
          type="email"
        />
        <Label for="exampleEmail">
          Email
        </Label>
      </FormGroup>
      {' '}
      <FormGroup floating>
        <Input
          id="examplePassword"
          name="password"
          placeholder="Password"
          type="password"
        />
        <Label for="examplePassword">
          Password
        </Label>
      </FormGroup>
      
      <Button>
        Submit
      </Button>
    </Form>

           
    );
    
}
